title.narrative: HEALTH SERVICE DELIVERY

description.narrative: Relevant MDAs and LGAs develop, implement and monitor policies, plans and budgets for effective delivery of health services, which contributes to Child Health, Health Systems Strengthening, Maternal And Newborn Health. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Improved and equitable use of high impact Maternal, Neonatal, and Child Health (MNCH) and nutrition interventions and promotion of healthy behaviours and nutrition practices
